media.ext_alt_text:
A yellow car skids down a narrow bridge as the driver slams on the brakes. 
An orange car falls from the sky with great velocity, narrowly missing the yellow car as it is about to smash into the bridge. 
Straight ahead of the yellow car, a vibrant red truck with its empty trailer still attached, also comes down from the sky.
Far off into the distance, a fourth vehicle is experiencing a temporary feeling of weightlessness before it will soon come to an abrupt halt.
Beyond all of these vehicles, beyond the visible end of the bridge, an ominous translucent red circle hovers in the sky, containing within its inner boundaries a blue icon of a sportscar.
